  "Notes": [
    {
      "Text": "Security update for gimp",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for gimp fixes the following issues:\n\nChanges in gimp:\n\n- CVE-2026-4150: Fixed PSD file parsing integer overflow vulnerability (bsc#1259979)\n= CVE-2026-4151: Fixed ANI file parsing integer overflow vulnerability (bsc#1259983)\n- CVE-2026-4153: Fixed PSP file parsing heap-based buffer overflow vulnerability (bsc#1259984)\n- CVE-2026-4154: Fixed XPM file parsing integer overflow vulnerability (bsc#1259986)\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
    },
